  <p class="section-label">Pricing</p>
  <h2 class="section-title" style="max-width:100%">Simple, honest pricing.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub" style="max-width:100%;margin:0 auto 0">No hidden fees. No surprise bills. Cancel anytime.</p>

  <div class="pricing-grid">
    <div class="price-card">
